title: Dream Cafe - Uptown
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Southwestern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Brunch, lunch, and dinner. Has ovo-lacto vegetarian items and a few dishes can be made vegan like a stiry fry with brown rice (choose tofu). A second Dallas location at 5100 Belt Line Rd Ste 732.
